



To Captain John Mercer, of the Virginia Regiment.
[Fredericksburg, 1 November 1755]



You are hereby ordered to Rendezvous at Alexandria the first Day of December, with all the men you can raise by that time. Given &c. at Fredericksburg, November 1st 1755.

G:M. aid de camp


N:B. Captain Joshua Lewis is allowed to the 1st of December, to Rendezvous at Alexandria.

